snippet.title: Early Tomb Raider Teaser (1996)
snippet.description:
Check out an early option for Tomb Raider’s title screen and logo treatment by Core Design. #TombRaider20

Footage preserved by Planet Lara. Music from Nathan McCree's original Tomb Raider soundtrack added by Crystal Dynamics.
